reprocess_table_row

Source: R/reprocess_table_row.R
reprocess_table_row.Rd

regenerate a row in the catalog

Usage

reprocess_table_row(path_to_ras_dbase, excel_row)

Arguments

path_to_ras_dbase

The path to the top level folder of the ras_catalog structure

excel_row

if you opened this up in excel (1 based index) the row you want to process

Value

updates a row to hopefully place the model in a better space
